raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"dorm_hallway\")
do heart(1)
Player: Hey Mabes, did you tour around?
Player: Find the grocers?
Player: Mabes? 👀
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do online_status(\"mabel\", \"online\")
Mabel: OMG
Mabel: I just got home
Mabel: It's almost 10!!
Player: Wow you're up late
Player: Partying already? 😏
Mabel: NO 😭
Mabel: Okay so
Mabel: I went to find the grocery store like I said
Mabel: And I found it!
Mabel: img: mabel/5
Mabel: Success!
Mabel: But then on the way back...
Mabel: I got lost 🥺
Player: Oh no
Mabel: And it was dark
Mabel: And I got MORE lost
Mabel: And I started to panic a little
Mabel: Thought: AND I wanted to cry
Mabel: My heart's still racing honestly
- Are you okay?
	Player: Are you okay?
	Player: That sounds scary
	Mabel: I'm okay now
	Mabel: Just shaken up from all these sudden changes and the new environment
	- If you want to talk about it or call, I'm here [#love]
		set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
		Player: If you want to talk about it or call, I'm here
		Mabel: 🥰
		Mabel: PinkThought: Just marry me already seriously
		Mabel: I appreciate that so much
	- Good to know
		Player: Good to know
		Mabel: Thanks for asking ❤️
- At least you made it back [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: At least you made it back!
	Player: That's the important part
	Mabel: Thought: I thought you'd be a little more worried
	Mabel: Yeah true
do heart(0)
Mabel: I almost had to ask a stranger for directions omg
- Oh no not a stranger!
	Player: Oh no not a stranger!
	Mabel: SCARY RIGHT?
	Player: You never know which ones turn into monsters at night
	Player: 👹
	Mabel: Eeeek, don't say that!! 😱
- You'll survive that lol
	Player: You'll survive that lol
	Mabel: I might but they might start waving at me when I run into them again
	Mabel: And I might have forgot who they are 😭
Player: The horror
Mabel: Omg 😣
Mabel: But then I remembered the phone you got for me shows all the locations on campus
Mabel: So it pointed me back to the dorms phew
Mabel: Made it home safe 😌
Mabel: Do you think I'm a weenie?
Mabel: Still scared of the dark and strangers at my age 😣
- You're fine!
